title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 22 2021
itunes:title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Nov 22 2021
description:
Reaction to the Rittenhouse verdict and tragedy at a Christmas parade in Wisconsin. Dr. Scott Atlas, former advisor on the pandemic to the president, explains how the current administration is botching their covid response. The part of the story no one is talking about regarding the parade massacre. Why Clay and Buck's anti-woke audience is exploding.
